Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Combine pumpkin, 3 tablespoons of the SPLENDA(r) Brown Sugar Blend, butter, cinnamon and nutmeg in medium saucepan. Cook over medium heat, stirring occasionally, until mixture comes to a boil. Reduce heat to low; cook 1 to 2 minutes. Pour hot mixture into an ungreased 1 1/2-quart casserole dish. Combine remaining 1 tablespoon of the SPLENDA(r) Brown Sugar Blend and pecans in small bowl. Sprinkle over pumpkin. Bake 5 to 10 minutes or until browned.